{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "幸村 第4话 毅力！化解危机！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01",
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "充分理解家臣的优缺点\\n并予以信任的幸村\\n与甚八建立了牢固的信赖关系。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01",
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "幸村之后也勤于与家臣交流……\\n人们纷纷慕名而来，不知不觉间，\\n幸村拥有了众多各有才能的家臣。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01",
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "众多值得信赖的家臣之中\\n有一位忍者名为佐助。\\n某天，佐助带来了一条重要的消息。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "诶？骸众的余党！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "没错。从他们的动向来看，\\n很有可能正在为进攻这座\\n城池而策划！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "骸众……就是那帮复活月读，\\n谋划倒幕的家伙啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "竟然妄图进攻龙氏的城池……\\n看来他们还没有放弃倒幕。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "听说之前有人袭击了\\n幸村大人和甚八……\\n也许那帮人也是骸众。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "唔……\\n确实有这个可能。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "也就是说他们是同伙吗！\\n好嘞！\\n这次也要好好教训他们一顿！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "那就由小人来准备应敌之策吧，\\n刚好心生一计。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "好！交给你了，甚八！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大家一定要齐心协力\\n守护好这座城池！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "不久之后——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众1",
            "context": "根据打探，幸村城后方防守薄弱。\\n我们可以从那里下手……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众2",
            "context": "唔……嗯！？喂！\\n这城的样子和之前的调查不一样啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众1",
            "context": "什么！？这、这是……\\n城墙外面又多了一个小城！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "他们果然选择了这座城的弱点。\\n还好提前布下对策。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "唉……不过你的主意可真是强人所难，\\n竟然要让人在十天内建出一座支城。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "但大家最后不是办到了吗！\\n幸儿的家臣们真的都很厉害呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "我等臣下自当为幸村大人\\n赴汤蹈火在所不辞！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "接下来才是此计的关键！\\n我们闭城不出，\\n一点点削弱敌军的战力！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众1",
            "context": "石、石头！？哇啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "唔！快撤！回去重整旗鼓！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "噢噢！\\n那帮家伙夹着尾巴逃跑了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "干得好！城池守住了！\\n我们胜利啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "（一见形势不利就毫不犹豫地\\n撤退……看来敌军也不笨啊。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "（这一战……\\n看来还会有一番波折……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众2",
            "context": "啧……怎么办？\\n那座城现在已经没有弱点了。\\n这下该怎么攻陷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "不……还有办法。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "正所谓兵来将挡，水来土掩。\\n一计自有一计破。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "敌袭！那帮人又来了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "冷静点，\\n这次也用投石来……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "可他们瞄准没有\\n投石器的地方攻来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "毕竟是匆忙建造的支城，\\n投石器没能覆盖所有死角……\\n而那里便是支城的薄弱点……只是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "嗯，真让人费解，\\n为什么他们能\\n准确地找到这个薄弱点……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "支城之外应该是看不到\\n投石器的位置的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村军士兵1",
            "context": "那、那个……这难道是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村军士兵2",
            "context": "嗯……恐怕是我们之中\\n有通敌的叛徒……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "（不好，军心开始动摇了……\\n这样下去士气会大受影响……\\n可究竟该如何才能……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不要惊慌！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01",
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村军士兵们",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "这里没有什么叛徒！\\n大家都是幸儿信任的伙伴！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村军士兵1",
            "context": "幸、幸村大人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村军士兵2",
            "context": "可是……既然如此，\\n敌人又为什么能得知\\n支城的薄弱点……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "那是因为……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "这个东西！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "鸟变成了光！？\\n幸村大人，这究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "这是阴阳师们所驱使的式鬼。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "晴明以前说过，\\n这种式鬼常用于侦察。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "原来如此。敌人就是靠这个侦察\\n支城内部并发现弱点的啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "所以说根本没什么叛徒！\\n好了！大家重新打起精神，\\n一同击退敌军吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不用担心！\\n幸儿相信大家，\\n我们一定能够取得胜利！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "（不愧是幸村大人……\\n您那坚定不移的信念\\n再一次拯救了我们。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "（不仅如此，\\n士兵们在幸村大人的鼓舞之下\\n士气无比高涨，如今正是时机！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "幸村大人，如今之势，\\n退敌之策当属……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "噢！好！\\n就按此计行事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "此时正是转守为攻之时！\\n大家随我一同出城！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "唔……式鬼没有反应了。\\n难道是被发现了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "算了。已经获得了所需情报。\\n接下来只要集中火力攻击薄弱点，\\n早晚能攻下支城——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "怎、怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "冲啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "敌军都聚集在支城的薄弱点！\\n要包围他们易如反掌！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众2",
            "context": "什、什么！？\\n他们竟然会出城迎战！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "啧……不要慌！准备迎击！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "天真！在幸村大人的鼓舞之下，\\n我军士气高涨，早已势不可当！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佐助",
            "context": "大家跟上！我们已经胜券在握！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大家好样的！\\n好嘞！幸儿也不会落后的哦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众3",
            "context": "呃啊！？该、该死……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "幸村大人英武！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120154_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "甚八",
            "context": "敌人皆已伏诛。\\n我方则无人伤亡……\\n我们大获全胜了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "太好了！\\n这都多亏了大家的努力！\\n谢谢大家！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "为胜利欢呼吧！一～二……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村等人",
            "context": "噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}